oyd]], English race car driver * 1984 &ndash; [[Duane Solomon]], American runner *[[1985]] &ndash; [[Kamani Hill]], American soccer player *[[1986]] &ndash; [[Tom Huddlestone]], English footballer *[[1987]] &ndash; [[Matthias Schwarz]], German footballer *[[1989]] &ndash; [[Salvador Sobral]], Portuguese singer and Eurovision winner *[[1990]] &ndash; [[Ayele Abshero]], Ethiopian runner * 1990 &ndash; [[Bastiaan Lijesen]], Dutch swimmer * 1990 &ndash; [[David Archuleta]], American singer-songwriter *[[1994]] &ndash; [[Adam Peaty]], English swimmer <!--Please do not add yourself or people without Wikipedia articles to this list. No red links, please. Do not link multiple occurrences of the same year, just link the first occurrence. Do not trust "this year in history" websites for accurate date information.-->
